	<shortDescription></shortDescription>
	<descriptionlist>
		<description>Replaces the "Today" view with an app of your choice. Originally made by Nepeta. Rewritten for iOS 13 by nicho1asdev.</description>
		<description>Keep in mind that this package is in beta, issues or bugs may be there. If you find any, please contact me on Twitter @itsnicho1as.</description>
		<description>Choose any application you want from settings.</description>
		<description>Options to configure from settings.</description>
		<description>KNOWN ISSUES: Keyboard will not appear in the Konban view.</description>
	</descriptionlist>
